headline: Cybèle Idelot's Ile-de-France adventure: from Hollywood childhood to kitchen gardens
description: 'Chefs' gardens' (1/5). The 50-year-old chef transformed a former coaching inn in Yvelines, just outside of Paris, into a domain that now welcomes guests to bed-and-breakfast rooms, a bistronomic restaurant, and above all, a vegetable garden that allows the restaurant to be self-sufficient.
